  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 7000000000001
    m_Localized: Escalating international conflicts have led nations to increase defense
      spending, boosting heavy arms demand.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000000002
    m_Localized: A sudden craze for the latest vehicle models has cleared out dealer
      inventories worldwide.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000000003
    m_Localized: A revolutionary new engine design has revitalized the aerospace industry.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000000004
    m_Localized: Supply chain disruptions halted semiconductor production, driving up
      component prices.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000000005
    m_Localized: A worldwide shopping bonanza has spiked demand for gadgets and home
      essentials.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7000000000006
    m_Localized: Global economic instability has driven a massive surge in demand for
